2 SMF
.BR
SMF (FB7) - line-mode small feature scan (macro)
.BL
Perform a small feature scan in line mode.
A large scan is performed and an attempt is made to identify
a closed feature in the measured data. If a feature is
found it is displayed in refresh and can be accepted using END (FB12).
.BL
