2 ONE
.BR
ONE (FB3) - (macro)
.BL
Used to guide the track follower through difficult passages.
If  the  track  follower  is  stuck  for some reason:
.BL
.LM+5
Press ONE
.BR
Point the tramlines in the right direction
.BR
Press GO
.BR
Select the correct track segment with NXT
