.BR
NXE -  get next edge-mode small feature
.BL
If more than one edge-mode small feature has been found in a scan
(see ESF), NXE (FB8) enables the user to cycle through them in
turn. When the required feature is highlighted in refresh, it
can be accepted using END (FB12). All the other found objects
are 'dropped' and must be scanned for again.
.BL
